data.description: $50,000 renovation credit with acceptable offer! Welcome home to your own private oasis in the exclusive Dunes West community! This 5 bed, 3.5 bath home features over 4500sf of living space. The open floor plan flows seamlessly from the soaring-ceiling family room to the updated chef's kitchen with granite countertops, 6-burner gas cooktop, stainless steel appliances, pantry, and wet bar. The downstairs master-suite is a true retreat, with a spa-like bathroom featuring an enclosed walk-in shower, floating bathtub, double vanity, and dual walk-in closets. Upstairs, 4 additional bedrooms and 2 full baths provide ample space for family and friends. The massive FROG is the perfect place for a playroom or home theater. Step outside to your private backyard, complete with a salt-water pool.
